{"id":185020,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vrilissia","text":"Vrilissia () is a small Greek city. It is near Athens in Attica. Almost 40,000 people live there. It is located at the northeastern edge of the metropolis of Athens. The city is accessed by Attiki Odos, the suburban railway and metro transit.\nVrilissia is an area with lots of squares and parks. It has a small forested area near the mountain of Pendeli.\nVrilissia is a twin city of Naples, Italy and Ottweiler in Germany. In Ottweiler, a main bridge is named after the Greek city.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Greece","surface_form":"Greek","offset":24},{"uri":"City","surface_form":"city","offset":30},{"uri":"Athens","surface_form":"Athens","offset":47},{"uri":"Attica","surface_form":"Attica","offset":57},{"uri":"Metropolis","surface_form":"metropolis","offset":144},{"uri":"Attiki_Odos","surface_form":"Attiki Odos","offset":190},{"uri":"Suburb","surface_form":"suburb","offset":207},{"uri":"Railway","surface_form":"railway","offset":216},{"uri":"Rapid_transit","surface_form":"metro transit","offset":228},{"uri":"Park","surface_form":"park","offset":289},{"uri":"Forest","surface_form":"forest","offset":311},{"uri":"Mountain","surface_form":"mountain","offset":334},{"uri":"Pendeli","surface_form":"Pendeli","offset":346},{"uri":"Twin_city","surface_form":"twin city","offset":370},{"uri":"Naples%2C_Italy","surface_form":"Naples, Italy","offset":383},{"uri":"Ottweiler","surface_form":"Ottweiler","offset":401},{"uri":"Germany","surface_form":"Germany","offset":414},{"uri":"Bridge","surface_form":"bridge","offset":444}]}